            a(href='https://github.com/paulbrzeski/kamigen')
              h3 Kamigen
            p A tropical cyberpunk game with supersonic aircraft. The setting is based on the island of Camiguin in Philippines as a tribute to my heritage and the wonder I felt when I visited as a kid.
          .column.six.wide
            a(href='https://github.com/paulbrzeski/kamigen')
