          .column.ten.wide
            a(href='https://github.com/paulbrzeski/manifold')
              h3 Manifold
            p A hybrid 2D/3D design tool, this is an experimental program to address the need for fast and efficient modelling for Three.JS scenes. The 2D vector component can also be used for general illustration and design needs.
          .column.six.wide
            a(href='https://github.com/paulbrzeski/manifold')
